::Spears::

She tried to dragged Striker inside.  She had gotten as far as the 
ramp and continued to try to drag him inside.  She looked at him,"You 
just hang on OK? I'm going to let you go. Not now."  She strained and 
pulled him inside.  She pulled him to the CR room and carefully put 
him into a chamber.  She layed him inside and shut the door.  She 
turned it on and looked at him inside. "Now, you get better and I'll 
just go and slag the bot who did this to you." She kissed the window 
on the CR chamber, wishing it was him, and ran back outside.
